{"tid":372424,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷舊推廣]mix足十年嘅音樂—decade mix by Flight Facilities","createTime":"2017-08-24T10:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T16:23:21.000Z","uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb06933a25aebf4140b5c5e00298eb8c1632b1a","tid":372424,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"小弟初次來到音樂台<br />\n為大家介紹呢個由Flight Facilities製作嘅decade mix系列，喺16年3月30日上載於Youtube上，由1972去到2012，每十年一首一個鐘嘅音樂，當中涵蓋30-40多首嘅經典歌曲，喺歌與歌之間用個人風格連接埋一齊，不失原作風味之餘又可以令人感到新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1972-1982<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YPg37aYz7tM&amp;t=107s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYPg37aYz7tM%26t%3D107s&d=yfeJQzqMfDuJ5kb8qnbXrpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=aeaf11bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YPg37aYz7tM&amp;t=107s</a><br />\n<br />\n1982-1992<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2p4fyCtQf7Q&amp;t=2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2p4fyCtQf7Q%26t%3D2s&d=yfeJQzqMfDuJ5kb8qnbXrpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c9aa7221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2p4fyCtQf7Q&amp;t=2s</a><br />\n<br />\n1992-2002<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qta8W5P26sI&amp;t=2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQta8W5P26sI%26t%3D2s&d=yfeJQzqMfDuJ5kb8qnbXrpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=75b429fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qta8W5P26sI&amp;t=2s</a><br />\n<br />\n2002-2012<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3jJt288zWDY&amp;t=2028s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3jJt288zWDY%26t%3D2028s&d=yfeJQzqMfDuJ5kb8qnbXrpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c863d98f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3jJt288zWDY&amp;t=2028s</a><br />\n<br />\n相信有人留意到每部影片嘅thumbnail都會見到一啲歷史名人，而呢個正正就係flight facilities值得欣賞嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢地會喺音樂入面quote返啲嗰段時期發生左啲咩新聞大事or名人講過嘅經典說話，聽落重要完全冇違和感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對Flight Facilities有興趣嘅可以follow佢地嘅youtube channel，佢地嘅一啲單曲同DJ music都幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdf3779d858144cf08f46b84c05b3ac9979aa91","tid":372424,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"仲有一個係淨係講2016嘅影片，自己欣賞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWk-RJbXHgY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCWk-RJbXHgY&d=yfeJQzqMfDuJ5kb8qnbXrpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b04587cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWk-RJbXHgY</a>"},{"pid":"cd5c4397bbace8b35975db1afd9466e6c8a8f531","tid":372424,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a9f934753ebae1bd39a044d7dcac1521a07809","tid":372424,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab53acf7e33c4e0abe584dda6f4827e2c1b16f6f","tid":372424,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5d353c8addc4b2424dd6a54e16185899a3fc06","tid":372424,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346ed28e18d110f9df247fff72961cc26c3cf9b3","tid":372424,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply